	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=1179><span id= >Diprimilas</span></a><br><span id=notbold>5 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Although in a finely tuned group we thrive at the later levels, if you find the time, there are always spawns that you can solo off of.&nbsp;&nbsp;At 35, you can easily solo the tree spec in Feerott, at 40+ you can kill the Happ at the Butcherblock port or the one in Lesser Fay, and after that Cyndreela at the Fear Portal is an easy kill.  Those places are usually camped, but they are definitely places where you can get some good XP soloing.  And even at the 35 range, some areas of SolB are nice to us enchanters :o)<br><br>Diprimilas<br>The weird enchantress of the Bristlebane Server<br></p>&nbsp;<br></td></td></tr>
