 2 spectres fighting each other, couple times stupid chars came to watch fight too close<br>even when gave warning to watch out. cause that spectre will rather hit PC than your pet<br>same thing allways when you use charmed pet or pet at all. PC comes first if he/she gets too close. and believe me they will blame you from their death.</p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
